name: Da Varanda #008
description: This is the octave photo, size 2895 x 1925 px - ISO 400 | 150mm | f/10 | 6 sec. One week, an apartment balcony and a camera. This series of photos is being produced from the balcony of my apartment. For 1 week, I will photograph the life that I can see from up here on the 10th floor. All will be minted in 100 editions at a low price and after the sale period, those that are not sold will be burned.
